race.description: Engineering By Stp Consultants Maiden F
race.comment: CYCLONE SKYLAH (8) hit the ground running off the tricky draw and gave a sight in front, boxing on well for a minor when second (19.61) at this track in a Maiden over 352m. Sure to be about the mark. NEMESIS (4) was a last-start winner from the inside at this track and distance (19.56), scoring by 0.8 lengths. Leading player again. SPECIAL ROCKY (6) pinged the lids from this draw last time and led throughout to win (19.66) at this track over 352m in a Maiden. Rates a leading chance again.  Something for the Multiples: GOLDSTAR EASTON (5)
